04:16.457 --> 04:25.397
â™ª whose arm doth bind
the restless wave â™ª

04:25.399 --> 04:31.937
â™ª o savior
whose almighty word â™ª

04:31.939 --> 04:35.374
â™ª the winds and waves

04:35.376 --> 04:40.379
â™ª submissive heard

04:40.381 --> 04:47.119
â™ª who bid'st
the mighty ocean deep â™ª

04:47.121 --> 04:55.127
â™ª its own appointed limits
keep â™ª

